Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.00,0:06:40.46,Default - 720,,0,0,0,,Sao anh ngồi ở đây thế? {Why are you alone?}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.46,0:06:42.79,Default - 720,,0,0,0,,Không mang hành lí thì đành chịu thôi. {I didn't bring my trunks.}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.79,0:06:43.84,Default - 720,,0,0,0,,Em thì sao?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.84,0:06:46.01,Default - 720,,0,0,0,,Hôm nay là ngày tự do. {We're on free time today.}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.01,0:06:49.55,Default - 720,,0,0,0,,Khi em trở lại nhà ăn sau bữa sáng thì \Nđã chẳng còn ai rồi. {When I got back to the cabin after breakfast, no one was there.}
